@host = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Claims
GET {{host}}/admin/claims
Authorization: {{token}}

### Get Claim by ID
GET {{host}}/admin/claims/1
Authorization: {{token}}

### Approve Claim
PUT {{host}}/admin/claims/1/approve
Authorization: {{token}}

### Reject Claim
PUT {{host}}/admin/claims/1/reject
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "remarks": "Insufficient proof of ownership."
}

### Create Claim
POST {{host}}/claims
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportId": 1
}

### Create Claim (Edge case - Invalid Report ID)
POST {{host}}/claims
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportId": 0
}
